 How to move Federated Database to End-User.

Example (see also Objectivity/DB Administration)

(0)
 setenv OO_FD_BOOT boot/path

(1) page A-18
oocopyfd -fdnumber 777 -dirpath /dath2/dbase/trk/calib/boot

